    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
一筆啓上仕候。然ニ天下勢云<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />。<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">扨肥後</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">兼御心安キ</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>庄村助右衛門度<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />面会、大兄に御目かゝり度よし。其故ハ云々――<seg rend="warichu" rendition="span">（<seg rend="overline_solid" rendition="em">此間ハ石田栄吉よりくハ敷申上ル御聞取ニて御返書書奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>願候。</seg>）</seg>○何卒、御思召の程御為<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>聞奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>願候。謹言。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">六月十日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</seg></seg>
木圭先生<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">才谷</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_4" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 4em">左右</seg>
